2034.text: I'm going to win anyway, so maybe I'll think of a line to say on the podium right now～♪

10015.text: Looks like there's an announcement! I wonder what it is～, I'm curious～♪

10018.text: I hear there's an event coming soon! I wonder if Kaichou will be there too～?

20000.text: Do I have to run today too? But I'm so tired～.

20001.text: Somehow, my body's not moving well…. Ugh～, I don't feel so good…!

20002.text: Hehe, the invincible Teio-sama is in top form again today! Don't topple over in surprise when you see me run, eh～?

20003.text: Hey hey, I'm feeling even stronger than usual today! I'm going to run faster! Faster faster faster!

20006.text: I'm ready! Hey hey, Trainer? You're still not～?

20007.text: Al～right, let's do it! Just watch me!

20023.text: Al～right, I'm in top condition! Hehe, Teio-sama's greatest legend isn't about to be broken this time!

20024.text: Watch carefully, trainer! I'll win in a flash; if you blink, you might miss it～

20025.text: I'm going to win anyway, so maybe I'll think of a line to say on the podium right now～♪

70001.text: Keep up the good work, Trainer! For the legend of the invincible Teio, you're absolutely necessary!

90003.text: Hey, have you seen Kaichou? Aw, I was thinking of having lunch with her today!

90004.text: Trainer, good job! Hmmm, you worked hard for me again today～♪

90005.text: Trainer's also out at this hour? I haven't done enough exercise yet, so I was just hanging around～.

90007.text: Hey～! Let's go catch a strong beetle～! Golshi has one too～!

91000.text: Of my class, I especially don't want to lose to McQueen. Whether it's tests or races, I'll beat her～!

91001.text: Let's go to the arcade together sometime! I'm confident I can beat Trainer at any game.

91002.text: Racing is good, but dancing is the best～! That's right, everyone thinks that both are amazing!

91003.text: Mom and dad call me all the time. They don't have to worry so much～.

91004.text: Hey hey, is there anything you wanna know? Hehehe… I'm a bit～ of an expert on academy gossip, you know?

91007.text: My goal is to be the undefeated, strongest, invincible triple crown Umamusume! In this outfit, I'll definitely make it come true!

91008.text: Look, look at this red cloak! And the sleeves' pattern too… ehehe, I asked to match them with Kaichou♪

91010.text: The student council room sofa is fluffy. I just take naps there but… Air Groove gets mad at me～.

91011.text: When I can't sleep, I listen to classical music. I get bored and fall asleep right away, I recommend it for Trainer too!

91013.text: When you jump off the diving board into the pool, it feels soooo good～! Next time I'm trying the highest one♪

92000.text: Hey～ what are we doing today? Hurry up, let's get started～!

92001.text: Trainer, what's next? Whatever it is, leave it to me!

92002.text: Streeetch! My body's so soft! It's squishy!

92003.text: Al～right, training time～! Watch my greatness closely!

92005.text: I'm not stopping until I become the strongest Umamusume! Of course, Trainer won't either, right?

92011.text: Let me try some reeeeally tough training! Pleease! Like Kaichou does!

400008.text: Our goal should be to reach a happy end where everyone's smiling!

400031.text: That CM with the 3 of them was so cool! It showed some neat places in the city, right? I can't wait to go play there!
